org.sd.cluster.job.work
Class DummyWorkServer

java.lang.Object
  org.sd.cluster.job.work.AbstractWorkServer
      org.sd.cluster.job.work.DummyWorkServer
All Implemented Interfaces:
WorkQueue, WorkServer
public class DummyWorkServer
extends AbstractWorkServer

A work server that serves only WAITING work.

This is typically used to allow a WorkClient with side-effects to run and stay alive while attached to this work server.

Author:
Spence Koehler
